<a name="3694"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Holiday Closures</div>
<br />


        The following holiday closures will be in effect this year.
        <ul>
            <li>The GES warehouse will be closed for freight deliveries on December 24-25, 2011 and January 1, 2012.</li>
        </ul>
    <br />
<img src="/images/framework/spacer.gif" width="1" height="20">
