<strong>Renaissance Meeting Space Exhibitors:</strong> if you wish to hang a sign or banner within your meeting room, please contact Noelle Williams at 703-907-7623 or <a  href="mailto:nwilliams@CE.org">nwilliams@CE.org</a> for ceiling height guidelines.<br />
